{"tid":1304683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔 好 錯 重 點","createTime":"2019-07-10T16:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T01:37:54.000Z","uid":93014,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c666cdaef45e3b1f1c0b52efdae3a03be6707804","tid":1304683,"uid":93014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"呢幾日貼牆 抵制大台 計劃光復同遊行<br />\n大家好似做左好多野咁<br />\n但係成效呢？<br />\n一枝寶礦力停廣告就可以即日上神枱<br />\n牆可以瘋狂貼 笑鳩人撕紙狗<br />\n大台取消show<br />\n<br />\n呢一堆野睇落好似好威做到好多野咁<br />\n但係事實有改變到咩？<br />\n五大（或者七大）講左咁耐既野有無係輿論戰或者國際曝光多左？<br />\n<br />\n要做杯葛紅底同tvb廣告商 但係唔係一野將撒廣告既放上神台 <br />\n貼牆可以貼完走 唔洗死守<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地人力物力應該幾時用 用係邊 係好重要</span></span><br />\n因為我地係同佢燒緊時間 錢<br />\n所謂「民意」話中間派唔會認同點點點係無謂<br />\n佢地係唔出黎 係唔肯幫拖 你幾和理非都無用 你點唔還手比狗咬都無用<br />\n我地諗番自己前線/ 鍵戰係幾撚辛苦 幾撚攰<br />\n烈士義士有幾多個人犧牲左<br />\n有幾多個後生仔出過去依家擔驚受怕有狗半夜拍門<br />\n諗緊自己如果真係比人拉要點做<br />\n<br />\n唔好重複雨傘既錯<br />\n大家唔可以坐係度數佔左幾多日而覺得光榮<br />\n大家唔可以貼memo 紙覺得民意係站係得地果邊<br />\n大家唔可以再不停送物資 靜坐覺得個政權會理<br />\n<br />\n個政權唔會怕<br />\n佢地怕咩？<br />\n怕我地搞分化佢地藍絲長輩圖攻勢<br />\n怕紅媒再洗唔到腦 拉攏藍絲<br />\n怕狗比人起底比人笑到癲左唔聽話<br />\n怕國際曝光 維尼無面 侵侵搞鳩佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家要攻 都要攻佢地怕既位<br />\n唔好再因爲小事 自我感覺良好就出一d無效攻勢</span></span></span><br />\n每講一次 XX要人<br />\n我地都消耗緊自己人力物力嫁<br />\n<br />\n我地行動全部都要對準佢地痛處<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe efficient<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBe effective <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d78e841a2996f4cc1b30d29c1cfd388835e537","tid":1304683,"uid":117892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:22:36.000Z","msg":"比起任何事 我只求每個義士平安歸隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n放人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c17e729c70bc77347ece4a871b879310a798ba","tid":1304683,"uid":240534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"對準政權"},{"pid":"6f00236e1723ff2272d1d610925dee402a03baba","tid":1304683,"uid":93014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:23:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd64a46db588858102e8d92ffd70c55671c1c61","tid":1304683,"uid":93014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f64127e0af6fa834c8106dad150d00bb44e750fa","tid":1304683,"uid":93014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2985eff185bd8d3a29472652bda3852e8b30a55f","tid":1304683,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62cf32cf845a4b66405e0f9875e8092151c8e2df","tid":1304683,"uid":155107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不敢忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrZ1Jix.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrZ1